commit.message: Fix incorrect configuration of BuildEnv instance in msi/exe bundlers. The directory for cooking app image when bundling msi/exe packages is supposed to be "${TMP}/image", but it was "${TMP}/image/${AppName}", which is correct for app image bundling, but not for msi/exe bundling. The issue doesn't have any functional impact.
FromParams: always set module path for jlink. Fix a regression from JDK-8333664.
